  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Subterranean Mineral",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "地下矿物",
    "TencentChinese": "地下矿物",
    "TraditionalChinese": "地底礦物"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Mined from <span class=\"name name-technology\">underground minerals</span>, cobalt is found in plentiful supply in caves and caverns. Useful in the manufacture of <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Ion Batteries</span>.<br><br>It is used in the creation of several technologies and structures, and can be processed in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to make the most of its inherent charge.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "钴大量存在于洞穴和山洞中，并可从<span class=\"name name-technology\">地下矿产</span>中开采。用于制造<span class=\"name name-commodity\">离子电池</span>。<br><br>用于创造几种技术和建筑，可在精炼机中加工使其内在电荷发挥最大效用。",
    "TencentChinese": "钴大量存在于洞穴和山洞中，并可从<span class=\"name name-technology\">地下矿产</span>中开采。用于制造<span class=\"name name-commodity\">离子电池</span>。<br><br>用于创造几种技术和建筑，可在精炼机中加工使其内在电荷发挥最大效用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "鈷是由<span class=\"name name-technology\">地底礦物</span>中採出，洞穴或其他地下洞窟中含量豐富。能用來製作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">離子電池</span>。<br><br>製造某些科技和結構時能派上用場，並能以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工，充分利用內含能量。"
  },
